<% content_for(:title) { @project.name } %>

<p class="text-center mb-8">
  <%= link_to "Back to Event", event_path(@project.event), class: "text-ezgreen" %>
</p>

<h3 class="text-2xl"><%= @project.idea.tagline %></h3>
<p>Submitted by: <%= @project.idea.submitter %></p>

<% if @project.links.present? %>
  <p class="mt-4">
    <%= link_to "Project Artifact", @project.links, class: "text-ezgreen hover:underline" %>
  </p>
<% end %>

<h4 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">Description:</h4>
<p><%= @project.idea.description %></p>

<h4 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">What resources do you need to be successful? (a skillset, person, access to a technology etc)</h4>
<p><%= @project.idea.resources %><p>

<h4 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">This idea will need access to Snowflake (data):</h4>
<p><%= @project.idea.snowflake_access %><p>

<h4 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">What value will this idea deliver?</h4>
<p><%= @project.idea.value_delivered %><p>

<h4 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">What is your goal for this idea in the hackathon?</h4>
<p><%= @project.idea.goal %><p>

<h4 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">How many "people hours" do you estimate it will take to plan, scope and demo?</h4>
<p><%= @project.idea.hours_estimate %><p>

<h4 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">Additional Comments:</h4>
<p><%= @project.additional_comments.presence || "None." %></p>

<div class="my-8">
  <%= link_to "Edit", edit_event_project_path(@project), class: "inline-block px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-ezgreen hover:bg-ezgreen-dark" %>
</p>
